Messages.Value: Thank you for calling ABC Travel, my name is Ethan James. How may I assist you today?
Hello Ethan, my name is Jane Smith and I have a complaint regarding my recent trip to New York City.
I'm sorry to hear that, Jane. What seems to be the problem?
My flight was delayed multiple times and eventually cancelled, causing me to miss important meetings in New York City.
I'm sorry for the inconvenience, Jane. Do you have your flight information and reservation number available?
Yes, my flight was on Delta Airlines, flight number 1234, departure date 02/10/2022 at 9:00am. My reservation number is ABC123.

Thank you for that information, Jane. I apologize for the inconvenience caused by the delay and cancellation. I can help you reschedule or receive compensation for the disruption. Which would you prefer?
I would like to receive compensation for the disruption, please.
Understood, Jane. I will work on getting you the appropriate compensation and follow up with you via email with the details. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Ethan.
